{"tid":1014063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女被誤診切兩腎臟　檢驗後發現根本沒患癌","createTime":"2019-02-09T00:07:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T03:21:09.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1f7ed981e96b0b3a44cbf590fc6859b2d220fc8b","tid":1014063,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T00:07:54.000Z","msg":"美國一名73歲的老婦，去年被醫生誤診腎臟癌，而開刀切除一對腎臟，後來得要洗腎維持生命。她原本已獲安排接受腎臟移植，但仍晚了一步，本月初心臟病發死亡。<br />\n福斯電視台（Fox31）報導，科羅拉多州的伍莉（Linda Woolley）去年3月被診斷「可能」罹患腎臟癌，同年5月接受手術切除兩個腎臟。但手術後，活體組織切片的檢查結果顯示，伍莉的腎臟腫瘤是良性，沒有惡性跡象。只是腎臟切除後，已無法放回體內，伍莉從此每周得洗腎三次，每次4小時，令她的生活大受影響。伍莉去年接受訪問時說：「我覺得他們欠我一個腎，絕對是。」她後來聘請律師，控告醫院。<br />\n手術後初期的健康情況，令伍莉無法列入腎臟移植等候名單，但家人透露，她去世前，已獲列入名單內。不過，平均等候移植時間要7至10年，而一般老人都不會排在名單前列。伍莉去年11月公開她的遭遇，希望其他人在確診前要雙重查證，不要重蹈她的覆轍。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190209/640_2cf89fc013478f1ade6ecb51d3b42163.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190209%2F640_2cf89fc013478f1ade6ecb51d3b42163.jpg&h=0b27441a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190209/640_09afd2ab5eca8c932ee5cfa1d3116553.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190209%2F640_09afd2ab5eca8c932ee5cfa1d3116553.jpg&h=26b3c30c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"351a78ba46fd1342f73de721cd44484dc46b333e","tid":1014063,"uid":70183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T00:11:01.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"b4d2995f149c63a197480ee05359792cefc20e8e","tid":1014063,"uid":10208,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T00:14:50.000Z","msg":"伍莉去年接受訪問時說：「我覺得他們欠我一個腎，絕對是。」<br />\n唔係啊，佢地欠你兩個腎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08b350e3265a7a41868f7c36db52e305a4a737f5","tid":1014063,"uid":113360,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T00:29:53.000Z","msg":"又估錯國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b0fd055e15e47140bb1e64e3026c5e4771f0be8","tid":1014063,"uid":39426,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T00:33:18.000Z","msg":"手術後，活體組織切片的檢查結果顯示，伍莉的腎臟腫瘤是良性，沒有惡性跡象。<br />\n<br />\n醫生都講明可能係腎癌，一般都係要切d組織再去驗，當中點解一下就成個切左先去驗跟本冇人知，手術多數都係病人同意下先做，做完發現冇事又黎事後追討責任"},{"pid":"3f0c24d92bee198692ad2fefca05dc3e86d1d0b1","tid":1014063,"uid":160916,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T00:34:58.000Z","msg":"所以 second opinion 真係好重要"},{"pid":"3f9098ef8633d15e3735d0f823e5550e17884620","tid":1014063,"uid":85722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T00:51:00.000Z","msg":"如果咁老有絕症，我會有得佢病發，<br />\n咁老返正都係等死，啲錢留比個仔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd5731cff839492ad1049a68309c0c66130258d0","tid":1014063,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f0c24d92bee198692ad2fefca05dc3e86d1d0b1","tid":1014063,"uid":160916,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T00:34:58.000Z","msg":"所以 second opinion 真係好重要"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T02:33:12.000Z","msg":"冇錯"},{"pid":"cc9ade7839bcecd0c7d020e05ebbf7a9b521e444","tid":1014063,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T02:35:09.000Z","msg":"間醫院要賠撚死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce2251ad4d0bee1554023b35c5deb225ec9f6f25","tid":1014063,"uid":77092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T02:37:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cee84d5750589cc1f47da2f23344abb5e5c3b279","tid":1014063,"uid":164838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T03:21:09.000Z","msg":"拎左去賣？"}]}